[Note "1:6+ \cs, fewer than 10 points"]
{South opens 1\H and West Doubles.   

After the intervening Takeout Double <b>2/1 is OFF</b>. If you had 10 or more points you would Redouble. So even with only 9 points you can bid 2\C without fear that South will think you have a strong hand.
South also knows everything mentioned above so he passes.}

